209
00:09:04,130 --> 00:09:06,160
Two China Policy?

210
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:07,240
One?”

211
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,420
Good question.

212
00:09:08,420 --> 00:09:09,759
Once upon a time,

213
00:09:09,759 --> 00:09:11,680
most countries recognized Taiwan,

214
00:09:11,680 --> 00:09:14,060
the Republic of China, or ROC,

215
00:09:14,060 --> 00:09:16,370
